OL,6,FThe ASLEF train drivers walkout is in
OL,7,Frelation to a dispute over pay, with a
OL,8,Fseries of strikes taking place between
OL,9,FTuesday 30 January and Monday 5
OL,10,FFebruary.
OL,12,FTrain drivers are also refusing to
OL,13,Fwork overtime between Monday 29
OL,14,FJanuary until Tuesday 6 February.
