OL,3,CTravel advice issued ahead of latest
OL,4,CASLEF train drivers strike
OL,6,FASLEF's general secretary Mick Whelan
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have given the government
OL,8,Fevery opportunity to come to the table
OL,9,Fbut it has now been a year since we
OL,10,Fhad any contact from the Department
OL,11,Ffor Transport. It's clear they do not
OL,12,Fwant to resolve this dispute.
OL,14,F"Many of our members have now not had
OL,15,Fa single penny increase to their pay
OL,16,Fin half a decade, during which
OL,17,Finflation soared and with it the cost
OL,18,Fof living.
