OL,3,CTravel advice issued ahead of latest
OL,4,CASLEF train drivers strike
OL,6,F"Train drivers didn't even ask for an
OL,7,Fincrease during the Covid-19 pandemic
OL,8,Fwhen they worked throughout as key-
OL,9,Fworkers, risking their lives to allow
OL,10,FNHS and other workers to travel.
OL,12,F"The government has now tried their
OL,13,Fold trick of changing the rules when
OL,14,Fthey can't win and brought in Minimum
OL,15,FService Levels legislation. But this
OL,16,Fnew law, as we told officials during
OL,17,Fthe consultation period, won't ease
OL,18,Findustrial strife. It will likely just
OL,19,Fmake it worse.
