OL,6,F"There's no excuse. The government and
OL,7,Ftrain operating companies must come to
OL,8,Fthe table with a realistic offer so we
OL,9,Fcan end this dispute and work together
OL,10,Fto ensure the future of our railways."
OL,12,FAvanti West Coast are urging customers
OL,13,Fnot to travel on the strike days.
