OL,3,CTravel advice issued ahead of latest
OL,4,CASLEF train drivers strike
OL,6,FAndy Mellors, Managing Director at
OL,7,FAvanti West Coast, said: "Our
OL,8,Fcustomers want to be out using our
OL,9,Fnetwork and it is disappointing that
OL,10,Fwe are once again asking them not to
OL,11,Ftravel on a weekend. We understand
OL,12,Ftheir frustration and can only
OL,13,Fapologise for the disruption to their
OL,14,Fplans.
OL,16,F"We'd encourage those able to do so,
OL,17,Fto take advantage of the ticket
OL,18,Feasement, and change their day of
OL,19,Ftravel. Alternatively, customers are
OL,20,Fentitled to a full fee-free refund."
