OL,4,CASLEF train drivers strike
OL,6,FRail Minister Huw Merriman said:
OL,7,F"Passengers are being targeted by
OL,8,FAslef's decision to go on strike,
OL,9,Fdespite union bosses having an offer
OL,10,Fon the table that would take train
OL,11,Fdrivers' average salary up to #65,000
OL,12,Ffor a four-day week.
OL,14,F"While the RMT, TSSA and Unite have
OL,15,Fall agreed deals for their members,
OL,16,FAslef's leadership isn't even putting
OL,17,Fthe fair offer on the table to a vote
OL,18,Fof their members.
